## ReadonlyKeys type

Gets keys of an object which are readonly

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript
export declare type ReadonlyKeys<T extends object> = {
    [P in keyof T]-?: IsFullyWritable<Pick<T, P>> extends true ? never : P;
}[keyof T];
```
